import { Component, OnInit, HostBinding } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; import { RealEstateDetailsModel } from './real-estate-details.model'; import { switchMap } from 'rxjs/operators'; import { ResolverHelper, IResolvedRouteData } from '../../utils/resolver-helper'; @Component({ selector: 'app-real-estate-details', templateUrl: './real-estate-details.page.html', styleUrls: [ './styles/real-estate-details.page.scss', './styles/real-estate-details.shell.scss' ] }) export class RealEstateDetailsPage implements OnInit { details: RealEstateDetailsModel; @HostBinding('class.is-shell') get isShell() { return (this.details && this.details.isShell) ? true : false; } constructor(private route: ActivatedRoute) { } ngOnInit(): void { this.route.data .pipe( // Extract data for this page switchMap((resolvedRouteData: IResolvedRouteData) => { return ResolverHelper.extractData(resolvedRouteData.data, RealEstateDetailsModel); }) ) .subscribe({ next: (state) => { this.details = state; }, error: (error) => console.log(error) }); } } Real Estate Details
